%% LawMitran — CI/CD Pipeline (GitHub Actions)
flowchart LR
    dev_local["Developer"] -->|push feature/*| pr{"Pull Request"}
    pr -->|CI: lint · tsc · test| ci_ok{"CI green?"}
    ci_ok -->|no| dev_local
    ci_ok -->|yes, merge to develop| build_dev["Build + push image<br/>(GHCR)"]

    build_dev --> deploy_dev["Deploy → Development<br/>dev.lawmitran.com (auto)"]
    deploy_dev -->|promote: merge develop→qa| build_qa["Build + push image"]
    build_qa --> deploy_qa["Deploy → QA<br/>qa.lawmitran.com (auto)"]
    deploy_qa -->|promote: merge qa→main + tag| build_prod["Build + push image"]
    build_prod --> gate{"Manual approval"}
    gate -->|approved| deploy_prod["Deploy → Production<br/>lawmitran.com"]
    deploy_prod --> smoke["Smoke tests + health checks"]
    smoke -->|fail| rollback["Rollback to previous SHA"]
